							<p>
								<name type="person" role="censor">Fra Luigi da Bologna Maggio</name>, a converted Jew working for the Inquisition as censor (active approximately 1590-1609): inscribed with his name, <date calendar="Gregorian">1599 </date> (folio 322v); see <ref target="Popper_1969" type="page">104</ref>. </p>
